#. §0: `def degree (G : Graph) (v : Nat) : Nat := (G.E.filter (fun e => incident v e)).card`
#. §1: `degree G v`
#. §2: `G`
#. §3: `v`
#. §4: `v`
#: Game.Levels.GraphTheory.L02_AddEdge
msgid "§0\n"
"§1 where §2 is a graph and §3 is a vertex gives you the number of edges which have §4 as one of their endpoints."
msgstr ""

